Class IsRefFromCheckConstraint

java.lang.Object
  drawnet.lib.ddl.constraints.Constraint

          drawnet.lib.ddl.constraints.IsRefFromCheckConstraint

public class IsRefFromCheckConstraint
extends CheckConstraint

A Constraint that checks if an element refers to the current element. Example: 'ref' is the name of the property (of kind ElementRefPropertyValue) of the current element that points to the element to check.
